{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":65571,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ずいぶん長く…………","translatedEnglishLine":"It's been quite a long time..."},{"lineNumber":65572,"originalJapaneseLine":"っ、こほ、ごほっ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"*Cough*, *cough*...!"},{"lineNumber":65573,"originalJapaneseLine":"不意に、ルートは咳き込んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"Suddenly, Lute started coughing."},{"lineNumber":65574,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっ、急におしゃべりしすぎましたか？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, was I talking too much all of a sudden?"},{"lineNumber":65575,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お水どうぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Here, have some water.\""},{"lineNumber":65576,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ご丁寧にありがとうございます。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Thank you for your kindness."},{"lineNumber":65577,"originalJapaneseLine":"　……ですがその、疲れたわけではありません」","translatedEnglishLine":"...But it's not that I'm tired.\""},{"lineNumber":65578,"originalJapaneseLine":"少し陰りのある表情で、ルートは微笑んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"With a slightly shadowed expression, Lute smiled."},{"lineNumber":65579,"originalJapaneseLine":"「私、死病にかかっているのです。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I am suffering from a terminal illness."},{"lineNumber":65580,"originalJapaneseLine":"　苦労して、起こして頂いて申し訳ないのですが、","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm sorry to have troubled you by waking you up,"},{"lineNumber":65581,"originalJapaneseLine":"　余命は三ヶ月ばかりと……」","translatedEnglishLine":"but my remaining life expectancy is about three months...\""},{"lineNumber":65582,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんだと？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What did you say?"},{"lineNumber":65583,"originalJapaneseLine":"　だが身体はマジックアイテムが作ったのでは……」","translatedEnglishLine":"But wasn't your body created by a magic item...?"},{"lineNumber":65584,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……IPボディは肉体を完全に複製するからな。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Because the IP body perfectly copies the physical body."},{"lineNumber":65585,"originalJapaneseLine":"　肉体にかかっている病気も複製した、という事だ」","translatedEnglishLine":"That means it also replicated the disease affecting the body.\""},{"lineNumber":65586,"originalJapaneseLine":"「む。むむむむ。美人が死ぬのは看過できん。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm. I can’t overlook a beauty dying."},{"lineNumber":65587,"originalJapaneseLine":"　シィル、魔法で治せないのか","translatedEnglishLine":"Sheel, can’t you cure it with magic?"},{"lineNumber":65588,"originalJapaneseLine":"「病気は魔法だと、あんまり効き目が……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Magic isn’t very effective against illnesses...\""},{"lineNumber":65589,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちっ、もったいない。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Tch, what a waste."},{"lineNumber":65590,"originalJapaneseLine":"　何か手段はないのか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Isn’t there any method...?"},{"lineNumber":65591,"originalJapaneseLine":"「パイアールが手を焼く代物だもんね……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It’s something even Paiarl struggles with..."},{"lineNumber":65592,"originalJapaneseLine":"　どうにかするって言っても……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Even if they say they’ll do something..."},{"lineNumber":65593,"originalJapaneseLine":"「病気の詳細が分からねば、如何ともしがたい」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"If we don’t know the details of the illness, there’s not much we can do.\""},{"lineNumber":65594,"originalJapaneseLine":"「病名はカスケードと、お医者様は仰っていました。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The doctor said the name of the illness is Cascade."},{"lineNumber":65595,"originalJapaneseLine":"　申し出はありがたいですが、不治の病で……」","translatedEnglishLine":"I appreciate the offer, but it is an incurable disease...\""},{"lineNumber":65596,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………え、カスケード？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Huh, Cascade?"},{"lineNumber":65597,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それって、ほっとくと手足痺れたり、","translatedEnglishLine":"Isn’t that the one where if left untreated, your limbs go numb,"},{"lineNumber":65598,"originalJapaneseLine":"　咳が止まらなくなったり……っていうあれ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"and the coughing won’t stop... that one?\""},{"lineNumber":65599,"originalJapaneseLine":"不意に、ミルが口を挟んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"Suddenly, Mil interjected."},{"lineNumber":65600,"originalJapaneseLine":"「え？　え、ええ……手足が萎え腐り、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eh? Y-yes... limbs wither and rot,"},{"lineNumber":65601,"originalJapaneseLine":"　次に内臓が死んでいくという……」","translatedEnglishLine":"and then the internal organs die off...\""},{"lineNumber":65602,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それ、治るよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That can be cured.\""},{"lineNumber":65603,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………えっ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...........Eh?\""},{"lineNumber":65604,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんだと！　マジか、ミル！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What! Seriously, Mil!?\""},{"lineNumber":65605,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うん。ずいぶん昔に治療法は見つかってて……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah. A treatment was found quite a long time ago..."},{"lineNumber":65606,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今は薬があるの。はいこれ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Now there’s medicine. Here, take this.\""},{"lineNumber":65607,"originalJapaneseLine":"ごそごそとポーチを漁って、","translatedEnglishLine":"She rummaged through her pouch,"},{"lineNumber":65608,"originalJapaneseLine":"ミルは一服の粉薬を差し出した。","translatedEnglishLine":"and Mil handed over a small packet of powdered medicine."},{"lineNumber":65609,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そ、そんなものが……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Th-That kind of thing exists...?"},{"lineNumber":65610,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あ、で、でも、頂くわけにはいきません。","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah, b-but I can’t accept it."},{"lineNumber":65611,"originalJapaneseLine":"　高価でしょうし、私には、なんの代価も……」","translatedEnglishLine":"It’s probably expensive, and I have nothing to offer in return...\""},{"lineNumber":65612,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おっと、代価なら払えるではないか。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Whoa, I can pay the price."},{"lineNumber":65613,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ぐふふ、その……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hehe, well..."},{"lineNumber":65614,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ランス、ストーップ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Lance, stop."},{"lineNumber":65615,"originalJapaneseLine":"　私の薬。私が好きにしていいよね？」","translatedEnglishLine":"It’s my medicine. I can decide what to do with it, right?\""},{"lineNumber":65616,"originalJapaneseLine":"「む……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm...\""},{"lineNumber":65617,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いーのいーの。高くないの。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It’s okay, it’s not expensive."},{"lineNumber":65618,"originalJapaneseLine":"　かかる人は少ないけど、風邪薬みたいなもんだし。","translatedEnglishLine":"Few people contract it, but it’s kind of like a cold medicine."},{"lineNumber":65619,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うち、薬屋さんなんだよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"My family runs a pharmacy.\""},{"lineNumber":65620,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However...\"}]}  ?>}  <|diff_marker||>END OF DOCIBILITY|>Assistant has translated all lines exactly as requested in the provided JSON schema. If you need more translations or further assistance, feel free to ask! Here's the translations for your reference:```json {"


